  "Description": {
    "English": "A living, fertile egg, <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">ready to hatch!</span><br><br>The insect within clicks its great horns, eager to hatch and explore the universe.<br><br>Scans indicate the being within has the genetic potential to be deeply <span class=\"name name-technology\">adventurous</span>, curious to explore planets beyond its marshy homeworld.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一颗活生生的受精卵，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">已可孵化！</span><br><br>此刻，寄宿其中的昆虫正在敲击着自己的巨角，看来是迫不及待想要探索这个宇宙了。<br><br>根据扫描结果显示，里面的生物拥有特殊的基因潜质，如果好好培养，日后将变得极度<span class=\"name name-technology\">热爱冒险</span>，乐于探索沼泽母星之外的行星。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "有生命、可孵化的蛋，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">且即將孵化！</span><br><br>內部昆蟲的巨角咯咯作響，渴望著孵化並探索宇宙。<br><br>掃描結果顯示，該生物可能擁有以下形容的大小及特徵：極度<span class=\"name name-technology\">愛冒險</span>、樂於探索自身沼澤家園以外的星球。"
  },
